## 📁 What This App Does

```
SOURCE CSV  →  CANONICAL LAYER  →  BUREAU CROSSWALK  →  DESTINATION CSV
PolicyHeader     12 Canonical Fields   ISO / NCCI / FL State   DestPolicy
ClaimHeader      14 Transform Rules    56 Crosswalk Entries    DestClaim
```

### Features
- ✅ Paste or upload **any** Policy or Claim CSV (Guidewire, Duck Creek, or custom)
- ✅ Applies all **14 transformation rules** (TR-NI-001 through TR-NI-014)
- ✅ Validates **ICD-10-CM** diagnosis codes against neurological reference (20 G-codes)
- ✅ **NLP classification** of TreatmentDesc to canonical TreatmentType
- ✅ Generates **7 downloadable CSV outputs**: Canonical Policy, Canonical Claim, ISO Bureau, NCCI Bureau, FL State OIR, DestPolicy, DestClaim
- ✅ Color-coded **Transformation Log** (✅ Success / ⚠️ Warning / ❌ Hard Reject)
- ✅ Real-time **stats dashboard** with record counts

### Lookup Tables Built In
| Table | Referenced By | Default |
|-------|--------------|---------|
| CoverageLUT | TR-NI-004 | STANDARD |
| PlanTypeLUT | TR-NI-005 | STANDARD |
| LossTypeLUT | TR-NI-008 | HARD REJECT |
| BenefitTypeLUT | TR-NI-010 | UNCLASSIFIED |
| ICD10_REF | TR-NI-011 | NULL (nullable) |

