## 🗺️ Pipeline Architecture

| Layer | Tables | Owner |
|-------|--------|-------|
| **Source** | PolicyHeader (ID=6), ClaimHeader (ID=7) | Underwriting / Claims Ops |
| **Canonical** | Canon_NeurologyPolicy, Canon_NeurologyClaim | Data Engineering |
| **Bureau** | ISO, NCCI, Florida State OIR | Compliance |
| **Destination** | DestPolicy (ID=5), DestClaim (ID=6) | Data Products |

