## 📋 Sample Data

The app includes pre-loaded sample data for immediate demo use.
You can also upload your own CSV files using the file upload buttons.

**Policy CSV columns required:**
`PolicyNo, NamedInsured, PolicyStartDate, CoverageCode, PlanType`

**Claim CSV columns required:**
`ClaimNo, PolicyNo, LossDate, LossTypeCode, AmountPaid, BenefitCategory, DiagCode, TreatmentDesc, ClaimStatusCode`

